general.desc: Guangxi Liugong Machinery Co Ltd is a construction equipment manufacturer that offers services to construction equipment owners. The products of the company include forklift, wheel loader, crawler excavator, wheel excavator, roller, motor grader, bulldozer, crane, concrete, mining truck, and skid steer loader.
general.short_desc: Guangxi Liugong Machinery Co., Ltd. is engaged in the production and sale of engineering machinery and related accessories in China. The Company produces loaders, excavators, road rollers, fork lifts, cranes, pavers, graders and skid steer loaders.
